{"tid":1537828,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"App Idea, 自動平安鐘","createTime":"2019-09-04T05:18:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T05:36:16.000Z","uid":226443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1315b4fa4a09fb3467ffe9eb67b0ae6f58c0d693","tid":1537828,"uid":226443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:18:32.000Z","msg":"見到好多兄弟比狗捉咗，都通知唔到屋企人。<br />\n我見到有個app可以比佢地一鍵通知晒你設定好嘅人，連位置錄音。但係如果真係比狗捉，你邊有機會按嗰一鍵。<br />\n<br />\n所以我有個idea，唔知有無呢啲app，就係自動報平安嘅。<br />\n<br />\n用家出去玩時，可以設定開啓報平安時間，例如6pm出去玩，如果12點我都未deactivate，就會自動send嘢比指定朋友。當用家12點前自覺已經安全或暫時安全，可以extend呢個時間。<br />\n<br />\nactivate咗報平安mode之後，會track低你嘅location ,同錄音。會一同send比你指定嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n如果用家已經返咗屋企安全，就可以deactivate，所有錄音同location record就會delete (用家想keep都得嘅）<br />\n<br />\n如果中途比人熄咗機，server就會base on 已經取得嘅location同recording send比朋友。<br />\n<br />\n有啲1999，希望有人明我講乜。"},{"pid":"cea3c1ac8a62fcd3994338ced3da92091521f34e","tid":1537828,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:18:39.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"ht